\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 In spite of heavy is duties many units have managed to organise well run education courses.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
It in regretted that many soldiers look upon education within the unit as just another fatigue. Some look upon it as an escape from soldiering.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
There has been some disappointment that the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 Fun College has not been able on various occasions to after sufficient vacancies.
\par 
