\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 On the whole has been very good.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 Amongst tps in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680  }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 PALESTINE there have been 8 cases of Infantile Paralysis (2 fatal; 4 cases of Typhoid (1 fatal) end a small number of malaria cases.
