\par 13.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406 FINANCE, PAY AND ALOWANCE}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li426\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin426\itap0\pararsid10164406 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406 (a) Officers. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
There have been so many different instructions in the period that many officers are confused as to the method of drawing their pay and allowances. 
\par 
\par Many Officers accounts are not up to data. There are a number of cases of officers having received no local Overseas Allowances three or four months aft
er arrival in MSLF. There are a few cases where officers are by Army Pay Office as opposed to by Agents of their having received no allowances or pay since arrival.
\par 
\par In some cases the fault may have lain with the unit In that through ignorance of local
 instructions their method of rendering appropriate casualties was incorrect; but in many cases the time lag and the look of payment can only have been the fault of the Pay Offices
\par 
\par (b) Other Ranks}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 The Star Classification Scheme is still in many cases difficult to interpret. There are still anomalies in certain arms \endash 
 particularly R SIGS, RAMC and RACC. RRME in particular will find difficulty in recruiting Regulars because of the better pay in sinner trades in civilian life. 
\par 
\par Many units report delay in obtaining verification of eon's balances.
\par 
\par One unit in particular - 662 Armd Tps Wksps - is greatly dissatisfied the CC states that he has lost faith in the Regimental Paymaster.
\par 
\par (c) General}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 For the single man the rate of pay and allowances i
s probably fair compared with the cost of living, For the married man separated from his family, life is extremely difficult.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 This formation has no experience of the cost of living for families in this theatre.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid16060283 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
\par 14. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406 MISCELLANEOUS, INCLUDING SUGGESTIONS}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
