\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li426\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin426\itap0\pararsid10164406 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 (a) The Infantry}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680  }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 Group System}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
The group system for infantry battalions does not appear to be functioning smoothly yet. There are still cases of Northerners being posted to southern groups, etc,.
\par 
\par (b) Recreational Clothing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 There are occasions, ev
en in PALESTINE, when the soldier desires to wear clothes other than what the Army provides. For instance, for lack of anything else, the average soldier has to play cricket in KD uniform. It is admitted that clothes are available locally, but at enormous
 cost.
\par 
\par A standard issue of certain articles of clothing, available on repayment at reasonable prices, would be greatly appreciated.
\par 
\par (c) Compassionate Cases}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10164406 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 Cases often occur of soldiers receiving telegrams from home saying, for example, 'Mother dangerously ill apply compassionate leave".

\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid16060283 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
\par It is}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 felt that more publicity should be given at home \emdash  (eg,. in the newspapers or at the cinema) \emdash  as to what evide
nce and action is required in these cases.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
It is also felt that practically all cases could and should come via the War Office. If this were the case it would mean that the case had been investigated on the spot and War Office could signal the brief facts 
and authorise compassionate leave at the same time.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 dome cases do happen in this way. Many do not, and valuable and perhaps crucial time, is wasted.}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 If}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid942680  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16060283 
this system were to be implemented it should be fairly simple to publicise the fact and to arrange a simple channel of communication eg:\emdash 
